\f0\fs24 \cf0 # Banking Database System\
\
## 
\f1 \uc0\u55357 \u56524 
\f0  Overview\
This project is a simple **banking information system** built using SQL.  \
It simulates a small banking environment with **customers, accounts, and transactions**.  \
The project demonstrates how to:\
- Design a relational database schema.\
- Insert and manage sample data.\
- Run queries to extract useful banking insights.\
\
