## 
\f1 \uc0\u55357 \u56522 
\f0  Example Queries\
Some of the queries included:\
- **Total Balance per Customer**\
```sql\
SELECT c.Name, SUM(a.Balance) AS TotalBalance\
FROM Customers c\
JOIN Accounts a ON c.CustomerID = a.CustomerID\
GROUP BY c.Name;\
}